descriptionHtml:
The new McDelivery App is here to satisfy your cravings with just a few taps.​
Discover new features that make ordering easier than ever.​

More ways to get your favorites​
Choose between delivery or store pick-up for yourself or for others. Planning for an event? Send simultaneous deliveries to multiple locations in just one transaction! ​

Deals just for you​
Get McDelivery-exclusive offers and promos! ​

Pay your way ​
Pay via cash on delivery or thru numerous cashless payments options like debit or credit cards, GCash, and PayMaya.​

Track your delivery​
Use our order tracker to check the estimated delivery time.
descriptionShort: The new McDelivery App is here to satisfy your cravings with just a few taps.​

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Enjoy an updated, modern interface designed to make ordering your McDo favorites easier! Choose the nearest store to deliver to your doorstep with the Map Pinning and Store Selection feature. In the area? Pick-up is now a fulfillment option! Check on your order status worry-free with an updated Order Tracker and Live Chat function!

Ordering via McDelivery App also gives you access to exclusive offers and promotions, so don't miss out!

The new McDelivery App is here to satisfy your cravings with just a few taps.​
Discover new features that make ordering easier than ever.​

More ways to get your favorites​
Choose between delivery or store pick-up for yourself or for others. Planning for an event? Send simultaneous deliveries to multiple locations in just one transaction! ​

Deals just for you​
Get McDelivery-exclusive offers and promos! ​

Pay your way ​
Pay via cash on delivery or thru numerous cashless payments options like debit or credit cards, GCash, and PayMaya.​

Track your delivery​
Use our order tracker to check the estimated delivery time.
